text: Antonio Reynoso (born May 9, 1983) is an American politician and community organizer. Reynoso is the Borough President of Brooklyn since 2022. He was a member of the New York City Council for the 34th district from 2014 until 2022. He is a Democrat. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from New York City Category:Brooklyn borough presidents
